TELEPHONE INDUSTRY -- LABOR RELATIONS; AMERICAN TELEPHONE &amp; TELEGRAPH CO; 
CONTRACTS; COMMUNICATIONS WORKERS; INTERNATIONAL BROTHERHOOD OF ELECTRICAL 
WORKERS 
</P>
