Times; Photo, Ruth Ketcham Devine, left, helps Edith M. Curl with her corsage 
before the ceremonies. Both are members of the Class of 1939. ; Photo, Donald 
C. Bridgman -- President, Class of '39 GARY AMBROSE / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
